{"tid":1655630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"懷疑有手足報夢","createTime":"2019-10-15T07:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T08:02:21.000Z","uid":207766,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"829c69f1ead9fb82990f855dd68a13ab8970f934","tid":1655630,"uid":207766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:15:09.000Z","msg":"問朋友借ac!<br />\n咁我本身都幾易撞到嘢嘅人<br />\n事源我琴晚發咗個夢<br />\n我起身之後 即刻打咗個冷震加起雞皮<br />\n感覺上個夢都發咗好耐<br />\n但我只係好清楚記得一個畫面<br />\n我嘅視角係企咗係一架黑色七人車後面<br />\n咁個車係泊咗係個對住海嘅岸邊<br />\n對面有山<br />\n然後隔離有條好大嘅橋 有車係上面經過緊<br />\n橋下面有個女仔坐咗係到 雙手抱住咗膝頭<br />\n低頭應該喊緊<br />\n然後有三個男人叉住腰圍住佢<br />\n離遠見到有個男人行個過嚟<br />\n我記得嘅只有咁多<br />\n<br />\n只後我一直對呢個夢念念不忘<br />\n我上網查<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ih2gPy1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fih2gPy1.png&h=73d64e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MUnK7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MUnK7v.png&h=991b50de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDllm同個夢嘅畫面一模一樣<br />\n但利申我冇去過呢條橋嘅下層<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理性討論下"},{"pid":"3daeb728ee2d097f8318a978c7b8a6e74f2c69ba","tid":1655630,"uid":207766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mi6tFHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmi6tFHj.jpg&h=e5d54302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗我見到佢地位置係呢到"},{"pid":"37496e6dd211accb56b85496f727766c633eddab","tid":1655630,"uid":207766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"同埋個時好暗 我只係離遠見到 應該係黑色長頭髮"},{"pid":"0f1a5b3fcbb7a5b7a95a56fa7d2646f5361da914","tid":1655630,"uid":295340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"真心理性討論<br />\n見手足你開過幾個post都關於手足初自殺<br />\n都有機會係日有所思 夜有所夢 <br />\n試下放底下電話一排 放一放鬆"},{"pid":"8a275b88eee2af996058b4dc6e6a84e4ad5cbfc9","tid":1655630,"uid":3172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":